      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CORLESS THE KING (1) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 320m (18.78). Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Should be very hard to beat this time. BLACKPOOL GIGI (2) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 1.3 lengths away in third (18.80) at this track in a Maiden over 320m. The form from her last run stacks up well. Leading player again. CHARLOTTE'S ROSIE (3) is on debut without trialling for this. Worth keeping a close eye on the market. CLEARED BULLET (8) is a Danita Marshall-trained newcomer by Feral Franky out of Maximum Cindy. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can sneak into the frame at his first appearance.",
